      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've seen enough specialists. they just give me more pills or tell me to live with it. there isn't a \"fix\" for this. it's just a slow decay. sometimes i look at it and it feels like the only kind thing left to do is just find a way to make the noise stop. like, why is there such a massive stigma around just wanting peace? it feels so much more merciful than this.",
